<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #058789; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f0ecc9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #058789; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    .warning { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê Password Reset</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.x.frontend_url %>/reset_password?reset_password_token=<%= @token %>" class="button">
          Change My Password
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p><small>Or copy this link: <%= Rails.application.config.x.frontend_url %>/reset_password?reset_password_token=<%= @token %></small></p>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>This link will expire in 6 hours</li>
          <li>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email</li>
          <li>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team</p>
        <p>Happy reading! üìñ</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
